title: Vivageneviv
author: Vivageneviv
content: This year’s FIFA Women’s World Cup has been almost unpredictable, the group stage especially had my bet slips cutting even before the start of games, lol. Fast forward to round of 16 and I was hitting it right with little efforts. Now the finals draw nearer and it gets trickier, I just need one correct score to hit the jackpot, you wanna help guys? What’s your take on the England vs Australia game?
